Key Features:
✔ Eloquent ORM – Database interactions using models.
✔ Blade Template Engine – Lightweight and fast templating system.
✔ Artisan CLI – Command-line tool for automation.
✔ Routing – Simple and flexible URL routing.
✔ Middleware – Controls HTTP request processing.
✔ Authentication & Authorization – Built-in authentication system.
✔ Queues & Jobs – Asynchronous task execution.
✔ Caching – Supports Redis, Memcached, etc.
✔ Event Broadcasting – Real-time notifications using WebSockets.




Concept	One-liner Explanation
Dependency Injection	Inject class dependencies via constructor or resolve them using Laravel’s service container.
Class Object Construction	Use the app() helper or type-hint the class for automatic instantiation by Laravel.
Polymorphism	Define an interface, create multiple implementations, and bind them in the service container for flexible dependency resolution.
